<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>1. This Competition is open to people aged 18 or over.</p>
<p>2. Employees or agencies of Inghams or their family members, or anyone else connected with the Prize Draw may not enter the Prize Draw.</p>
<p>3. Entrants into the Competition shall be deemed to have accepted these Terms and Conditions.</p>
<p>4. . To enter the Competition you must like the Inghams Ski Facebook page and also write the word ‘Enter’ into the comments underneath either of the following posts scheduled on the Inghams Ski Facebook page:</p>
<p>- Post 1 - Scheduled at 14:00pm on 05/10/2017</p>
<p>- Post 2 - Scheduled at 14:00pm on 12/10/2017</p>
<p>5. Only one entry per person per pair of tickets will be registered. Entries on behalf of another person will not be accepted and joint submissions are not allowed.</p>
<p>6. Inghams accepts no responsibility for entries that are lost, delayed, misdirected or incomplete.</p>
<p>7. Three winners will be chosen a random draw of entries, received in accordance with these Terms and Conditions. The draw will be chosen at random by Inghams. The draw will take place and the winners announced on the Wednesday 18th October 2017.  Each winner announced will receive one pair of tickets.</p>
<p>8. Inghams accepts no responsibility for any costs associated with the prize and not specifically included in the prize.</p>
<p>9. The winners will be notified by Facebook Message at the end of the Competition. If the winner does not respond to Inghams within 1 day of being notified by Inghams, then the winner's prize will be forfeited and Inghams shall be entitled to select another winner in accordance with the process described above (This winner will have to reply that day in order for the tickets to be assigned in time for the Ski and Snowboard Show). If a winner rejects their prize or the entry is invalid or in breach of these Terms and Conditions, the winner's prize will be forfeited and Inghams shall be entitled to select another winner. The winner will be announced on the Inghams Facebook page at the end of the Competition.</p>
<p>10. The winners will be contacted via Facebook Messenger and requested to supply their email address and the date in which they wish to attend the Ski and Snowboard Show.</p>
<p>11. The winners can choose to attend one of the following day:</p>
<p>- Thursday 26th October</p>
<p>- Friday 27th October</p>
<p>- Sunday 29th October</p>
<p>12. The prize is non-exchangeable, non-transferable, and is not redeemable for cash or other prizes.</p>
<p>13. Inghams shall use and take care of any personal information you supply to it as described in its privacy policy, and in accordance with data protection legislation.</p>
<p>14. Inghams accepts no responsibility for any damage, loss, liabilities, injury or disappointment incurred or suffered by you as a result of entering the Competition or accepting the prize. Inghams further disclaims liability for any injury or damage to your or any other person's computer relating to or resulting from participation in or downloading any materials in connection with the Competition.</p>
<p>15. Inghams reserves the right at any time and from time to time to modify or discontinue, temporarily or permanently, this Competition with or without prior notice due to reasons outside its control (including, without limitation, in the case of anticipated, suspected or actual fraud). The decision of Inghams in all matters under its control is final and binding and no correspondence will be entered into.</p>
<p>16. Inghams shall not be liable for any failure to comply with its obligations where the failure is caused by something outside its reasonable control. Such circumstances shall include, but not be limited to, weather conditions, fire, flood, hurricane, strike, industrial dispute, war, hostilities, political unrest, riots, civil commotion, inevitable accidents, supervening legislation or any other circumstances amounting to force majeure.</p>
<p>17. The Competition will be governed by English law and entrants to the Competition submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English courts.</p>
<p>18. Promoter: Inghams Holidays, Mountain House, Station Road, Surrey, GU7 1EX.</p>
</div>
